        <h2>3. The Software</h2>
        <p>Portwood DocGen is a document generation application that runs entirely within the Salesforce platform. It creates PDFs, Word documents, Excel spreadsheets, and PowerPoint presentations from Salesforce records using templates with merge tags.</p>

